In the last summer,
we were moving

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:52.640
four millimeters in 60 seconds.

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:55.780
Now we move 20
centimeters in 15.

00:08:55.780 --> 00:08:58.700
So we've made massive
improvements on these pullers.

